header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - National Championship

videos.headline: Stanford's Williams gets fired up after transition 3
videos.description: Kiana Williams is fired up after she drains a transition 3-pointer to give Stanford an early 12-3 lead over Arizona.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Stanford's Williams gets fired up after transition 3) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pellington gets the steal and fast-break bucket for Arizona
videos.description: Shaina Pellington tips the pass to get the steal and races down the court to flip in a fast-break layup to give Arizona a 21-20 lead over Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Pellington gets the steal and fast-break bucket for Arizona) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lexie Hull drains and-1 3 for Stanford
videos.description: Stanford's Lexie Hull gets the pass from Ashten Prechtel, then pulls up to drain a 3-pointer and draw a foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Lexie Hull drains and-1 3 for Stanford) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Pellington shakes multiple defenders for and-1 layup
videos.description: Shaina Pellington uses a hesitation move to freeze the Stanford defense as she makes her way to the basket for an and-1 finish for Arizona.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Pellington shakes multiple defenders for and-1 layup) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanford's Jones spins for and-1 bucket
videos.description: Haley Jones spins on her defender and draws the contact as she gets the and-1 bucket for Stanford.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Stanford's Jones spins for and-1 bucket) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanford wins national title after locking up McDonald in final seconds
videos.description: Stanford's defense holds firm on the final possession as Aari McDonald misses the game-winning shot and the Cardinal come away with a 54-53 win.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Stanford wins national title after locking up McDonald in final seconds) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Stanford wins national championship in a game that comes down to the final shot
videos.description: Stanford holds off Arizona late as Wildcats guard Aari McDonald's shot is off the mark, and the Cardinal win the national title.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Stanford wins national championship in a game that comes down to the final shot) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Relive the drama of the women's NCAA tournament
videos.description: Experience the excitement and relive the biggest moments of the women's NCAA tournament as Stanford goes all the way to become the 2021 champion.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Feature (Relive the drama of the women's NCAA tournament) 2021/04/04 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arizona's Adia Barnes delivers powerful message
videos.description: Arizona women's basketball coach Adia Barnes is proud to represent moms and Black women and is thankful for the opportunity to be on the biggest stage.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCW Presser (Arizona's Adia Barnes delivers powerful message) 2021/04/04
